item.title: Prayer bpn4925 in Vanuatu
item.description: *Ol fren blong God … oli sud givim sam samting, nomata i smol tumas. God i no save putum wan hevi long eni man we hem i no inaf blong wokem. Ol Senta mo ol biliva i mas givim sam samting long Fand…O fren blong God! Yu mas save gud. Taem yu givim sam samting, ol garen blong yu, ol wok blong yu, mo ol bisnis blong yu oli save kam antap big wan, mo ol gudfala samting i save kam long yu.
